  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Displaying Market Data</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loio0222d553088f4308e10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Displaying Market Data</h1><div class=\"body\"> <div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2><p class=\"p\">You use the function <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Display Market Data</span> (<span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">TBD3</span>) or program <span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">RFTBDF00</span> to create a list of the last market data that was uploaded as well as statistics concerning any errors that occurred.\n</p> </section></div> <div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Activities\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Activities</h2><ol class=\"ol\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">In the area menu, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Treasury and Risk Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Basic Functions</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Market Data Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Datafeed</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Display Market Data</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span>.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Enter your selection data for the market data you wish to display.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Execute</span>. The system displays a list of the market data and the error statistics.\n</p><p class=\"p\">You can now select market data to display the details.\n</p></li></ol> </section></div> <div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"More Information\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">More Information</h2><p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"4f3adadc862e2e4fe10000000a42189e.html\">Datafeed</a>\n</p> </section></div> </div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
